TextBody:
Chris,

Based on the Proxy logs Dev noted that we need to run the FS_UpdateProxy Job.

Netwrix Enterprise Auditor v11.6 > Installation > File System Proxy as a Service Overview > Upgrade Proxy Service Procedure
https://helpcenter.netwrix.com/bundle/EnterpriseAuditor_11.6/page/Content/EnterpriseAuditor/Install/FileSystemProxy/Upgrade.htm 

This will copy the new binaries to the Proxy from the 11.6.0.82 installation.

Please let me know how the next set of scans complete.

If the issue persist please re-run the Proxy script then uploaded the new zip file directly to the case as we did today.

As always, thank You for your time.

Dusty Grayson
